The article announces several nominations and appointments sent to the Senate. The nominations include James H. Anderson as Deputy Under Secretary of Defense, Nancy B. Beck as Chairman of the Consumer Product Safety Commission and Commissioner of the Consumer Product Safety Commission, Rodney K. Brown as a Member of the Farm Credit Administration Board, Richard Giacolone as Federal Mediation and Conciliation Director, Marvin Kaplan as a Member of the National Labor Relations Board, Robert Joseph Kruckemeyer as a Member of the National Council on the Humanities, Andrea R. Lucas as a Member of the Equal Employment Opportunity Commission, Lauren McGarity McFerran as a Member of the National Labor Relations Board, Jocelyn Samuels as a Member of the Equal Employment Opportunity Commission, and Keith E. Sonderling as a Member of the Equal Employment Opportunity Commission.